requirements:

users
   - client
      - login using gmail oauth2
      - can create tickets
   - user
      - login using system credentials
      - can view/process tickets
   - admin
      - login using system credentials
      - can create other users, departments, products, categores, support types

tech stack
   - front end
      - reactjs
   - back end
      - express js
      - pm2
      - mysql

setup
   - set user access
      - client: can create/interact tickets
      - user: can see/interact to all tickets
      - admin: have access to setup
   - categories
   - services
   - products (with warranty tracking and support history)